OL,3,CPM spends #80k redecorating blue No 10
OL,4,CTV room to make it 'politically
OL,5,Cneutral'
OL,7,FKeir Starmer has had the Downing
OL,8,FStreet media room redecorated at a
OL,9,Fcost of up to #80,000, in order to
OL,10,Fmake the blue room "politically
OL,11,Fneutral."
OL,13,FA No10 spokesman described the
OL,14,Frenovation as a "one off refresh" of
OL,15,Fthe room in Number 9 Downing Street,
OL,16,Fused for briefings with reporters and
OL,17,Fsome press conferences.
