OL,7,FThe blue panels which surrounded the
OL,8,FTV screen on the stage have been
OL,9,Freplaced by grey ones while the blue
OL,10,Fcarpet lining the stage has been
OL,11,Fswapped for one in various shades of
OL,12,Fgrey.
OL,14,FDowning Street insisted the money
OL,15,Fspent on the redecoration is a
OL,16,F"fraction of the previous
