OL,7,FBoris Johnson came under fire in 2021
OL,8,Fafter his redesign of the room cost
OL,9,F#2.6 million, designed to be more like
OL,10,Fthe White House briefing room, with
OL,11,Fdaily televised briefings.
OL,13,FDowning Street later scrapped the plan
OL,14,Fto televise media briefings, instead
OL,15,Fsticking with off camera briefings and
OL,16,Fusing the room for press conferences.
OL,18,FAt the time Labour called the plans a
OL,19,F"vanity project".
