OL,7,FOn Tuesday Downing Street confirmed
OL,8,FStarmer would be using the room, and
OL,9,Finsisted media spending has gone down:
OL,10,F"This government has made #80m savings
OL,11,Facross government communications
OL,12,Fcompared to the previous government."
OL,14,FStarmer has been making a number of
OL,15,Fchanges to the decor in Downing
OL,16,FStreet, including notably removing a
OL,17,Fportrait of former PM Margaret
OL,18,FThatcher.
